  <h3>Welcome to the</h3>
<h2>Royal Society <span class="em">of</span> Canada</h2>
<p class="double-line">¬†</p>
<p>The Royal Society of Canada (RSC) was established under an Act of Parliament in 1883 as Canada‚Äôs National Academy, the senior collegium of distinguished scholars, artists and scientists in the country.</p>
